\plain\f0\fs20\cf0{\*\bkmkstart Levovist5}An uncomplicated tubal patency study was performed using sonographic contrast.  No free fill and spill of contrast medium was identified along either fallopian tube, suggestive of bilateral tubal spasm or blockage.{\*\bkmkend Levovist5}\li0\fi0\ri0\sb0\sa200\sl276\slmult1\ql\vertalt\par
